蒂姆·兰贝西斯 (Tim Lambesis) 的副业项目因《我弥留之际》争议而失去鼓手https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-lambesis-side-project-loses-drummer-after-as-i-lay-dying-controversy-3813516?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tim-lambesis-在我弥留之际的争议之后，副项目失去了鼓手Surej SinghMon, 18 Nov 2024 02:18:33 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3813516 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在其他人上个月以“个人道德”为由退出乐队后，这位歌手现在是“As I Lay Dying”中唯一剩下的成员</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-lambesis-side-project-loses-drummer-after-as-i-lay-dying-controversy-3813516">在《As I Lay Dying》争议</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>后，Tim Lambesis 的副业项目失去了鼓手。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/as-i-lay-dying">《我弥留之际</a>》主唱蒂姆·兰贝西斯的副业奥地利死亡机器失去了鼓手布兰登·肖特 - 了解更多信息如下。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/poppy-interview-negative-spaces-jordan-fish-3812948">波比加重了沉重感：“坐在极端之间对我来说感觉非常完整”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月（10 月 24 日），贝斯手 Ryan Neff、吉他手 Ken Susi 和鼓手 Nick Pierce 均于 2022 年加入 Lambesis 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/as-i-lay-dying">As I Lay Dying</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/three-members-quit-controversial-as-i-lay-dying-citing-personal-morals-3806056">宣布退出乐队，理由是“个人道德”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/longtime-as-i-lay-dying-guitarist-is-the-latest-member-to-quit-the-band-amid-difficult-and-serious-situation-3808518">随后吉他手 Phil Sgrosso 离开</a>，他自 2003 年以来一直是圣地亚哥金属核乐队的一员，使得 Lambesis 成为唯一剩下的成员。当时，斯格罗索表示，乐队的离开是因为乐队不再为“任何参与者提供健康或安全的环境——无论是创造性的、个人的还是专业的”。在目睹了一些令人担忧的行为模式后，我意识到，凭良心来说，我不能再采取可能对这个领域的任何工作人员产生负面影响的进一步行动。” </p><figure id="attachment_3806062" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806062" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806062" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer.jpg" alt="美国乐队 As I Lay Dying 的 Tim Lambesis 于 2019 年 10 月 3 日在德国柏林哥伦比亚音乐厅举行的音乐会上现场表演。 （弗兰克·霍恩施/Redferns 摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/As-I-Lay-Dying-singer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806062" class="wp-caption-text">美国乐队 As I Lay Dying 的 Tim Lambesis 于 2019 年 10 月 3 日在德国柏林哥伦比亚音乐厅举行的音乐会上现场表演。 （弗兰克·霍恩施/Redferns 摄）</figcaption></figure><p>现在，《As I Lay Dying》中的问题似乎已经蔓延到兰贝西斯的阿诺·施瓦辛格主题乐队奥地利死亡机器上，鼓手布兰登·肖特宣布退出。肖特在 Instagram 上写道：“为了我的精神健康和个人信仰，并考虑到《我弥留之际》营和蒂姆最近的事态发展，这对我来说是不可避免的一步。”</p><p>肖特继续说道：“反复的承诺，无休止的循环‘我会做得更好’——这些曾经给我希望的话语——已经变成了一个破纪录，没有带来真正的改变。相反，我发现自己陷入了一种侵蚀我的信任和幸福的模式。这个循环已经渗透到我的个人生活中，以我无法再忽视的方式影响着我的心理健康。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCaF24iz53v/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="