-to-prevail">Slaughter to Prevail 乐队</a>的 Alex Terrible 和前 Lorna Shore 歌手 Tom Barber 的客串演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3808522" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3808522" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3808522" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3808522" class="wp-caption-text"> 《当我弥留之际》的蒂姆·兰贝西斯。图片来源：Joey Foley/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/as-i-lay-dying-2-2-1240182">2014年，兰贝西斯因密谋杀害妻子而被判处六年监禁</a>。他承认向一名冒充杀手的警察支付了 1000 美元（630 英镑）以杀害他当时的妻子梅根·兰贝西斯（Meggan Lambesis）。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lay-dying-frontman-tim-lambesis-speaks-first-time-since-jailed-conspiracy-commit-murder-2177518">2016 年 12 月发行后</a>，兰贝西斯在乐队的官方 Facebook 页面上发表了一份冗长的声明，为自己的行为“向所有人道歉”。</p><p>这位歌手随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lay-dying-return-frontman-tim-lambesis-jailed-plotting-murder-wife-new-song-tour-2336899">于 2018 年与圣地亚哥乐队重聚</a>，后者发行了六年来的第一首新歌《My Own Grave》，并宣布了当年夏天返校演出的细节。长期吉他手 Nick Hipa 将于 2020 年离开乐队，鼓手 Jordan Mancino 和贝斯手 Josh Gilbert 将于 2022 年离开乐队。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-lambesis-side-project-loses-drummer-after-as-i-lay-dying-controversy-3813516">在《As I Lay Dying》争议</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>后，Tim Lambesis 的副业项目失去了鼓手。</p> ;
